Cell.Text: So, what say you, esteemed one?

Delightful. I am truly grateful for your willingness to share your expertise. | Together, we'll embark on a journey into the veiled corners of magic, weaving threads of forbidden lore into our reality. | We'll require a dedicated laboratorium for our studies; can you provide such a facility?
G|Most certainly. With our combined knowledge, we shall uncover the symphony of pleasures and secrets that await us. | I'll see you there.
G|Understandable. You can find me here, in the Arcanaeum. I long for the days of our cooperation.

Node.Caption: SM_Quest_Adriette_Intro6: I'll procure such a facility and return to you then.

Cell.Text: G|Of course, esteemed conjurer. Take the time you need to weigh the intricacies of our endeavor. | May your contemplations be as enlightening as the hidden paths we seek to tread.

Node.Caption: SM_Quest_Adriette_Intro7: I'll consider your request. Until then.

Cell.Text: [S] Greetings. I trust you have received my missive. I am Adriette Ganewald, a seeker of the arcane arts like you. | In my pursuit of unraveling the hidden secrets of conjuration, I have acknowledged the alluring presence of Dremora Mistresses. | It is said that you, esteemed conjurer, have summoned such captivating beings before. | I beseech you, guide me through the intricate dance of conjuration so that I may also weave their essence into our realm. | In return, I offer not only my gratitude, but the prospect of expanding our understanding of the Daedric forces that bind Nirn.

Cell.Text: A Breton by birth, I found solace and purpose within these ancient walls, before these arcane tomes. | My heart yearns for the enigmatic depths of conjuration, a pursuit that has earned me the reputation of an eccentric recluse. | Yet, beneath the surface, lies a relentless curiosity, a desire to breach the boundaries of the known. | But enough about me. The true dance awaits us in the embrace of the Dremora Mistresses. Will you be my guide?

Node.Caption: SM_Quest_Adriette_IntroTalk1Topic: I'd like to know more about yourself.

Cell.Text: My motivations are twofold: scholarly fascination and personal yearning. | Summoning these beings would unravel the tapestry of conjuration's intricacies, advancing my knowledge to unparalleled heights. | Yet, if you would truly value my honesty, there exists a darker thread... | ...an allure of forbidden pleasures, a whispered promise of indulgence that draws me, as a moth to flame. | You understand these implications, do you not?

Node.Caption: SM_Quest_Adriette_IntroTalk2Topic: What are your motivations for conjuring Dremora Mistresses?

Cell.Text: In exchange for your guidance, I offer a mutually beneficial alliance. | Have you not indulged in the dark pleasures provided by your Dremora Mistress? | With my knowledge of obscure conjuration lore, I can aid you in refining your mastery over this subject. | Your personal harem of Dremora Mistresses; that is the promised destiny of this endeavor.

Node.Caption: SM_Quest_Adriette_IntroTalk3Topic: More precisely, what are you offering me in return?
